{"tid":183414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"城大新碩士課程 教人養龍蝦","createTime":"2017-04-02T05:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T16:21:44.000Z","uid":35790,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a0ec25fb3f5c1b7af4796f430804df49f3a369d0","tid":183414,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:33:39.000Z","msg":"城大新課程 教人養龍蝦<br />\n香港城市大學轄下的城大動物醫學院將於新學年開辦首屆獸醫學學士課程，以及<span style=\"color: red;\">水產及獸醫衞生學碩士課程</span>，培訓水產養殖專才。<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170402/00176_014.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170402%2F00176_014.html&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=3ca41614\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170402/00176_014.html</a>"},{"pid":"7e3b9fe7d09715c063a127e45d1229f061593029","tid":183414,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451de25590eaebcf6767f2309e29887ae9278c7b","tid":183414,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:37:53.000Z","msg":"獸醫好似巨多人爭"},{"pid":"752554e82ab8a05b25f3dcf0862dfb21029ec6ab","tid":183414,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:38:41.000Z","msg":"神大 仲有核能碩士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"892896d4de727d58c3a1d24e2e067668df0736b1","tid":183414,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:42:19.000Z","msg":"吓? 有多出奇?<br />\n<br />\n水產養殖一直都係好專門既研究<br />\n<br />\n外國有好多大學有呢d課程, 有乜問題?"},{"pid":"433e53a8147c5e3b6f74042cdac8adbf2bcbc4fa","tid":183414,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:42:44.000Z","msg":"洗鬼讀咩 以家捉魚個d人有幾多人讀過書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"120a682484c9e8c677a5067a784a6239b1b44bb3","tid":183414,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:42:56.000Z","msg":"好揾錢"},{"pid":"ededd3836a3bf7e7d5f240a0e6af8db57d83b77a","tid":183414,"uid":683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:43:00.000Z","msg":"神奇水馬騮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e5b11089c12a22e716d8581a2fcfe10035c631b","tid":183414,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:44:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b3591f2eb6747c0c1648a4090f4fc979920e1e72","tid":183414,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:45:37.000Z","msg":"問城大校委咪知<br />\n大大隻養住"},{"pid":"81c154d713335a0753dd58b4b2747b63ed4c7030","tid":183414,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:47:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>獸醫好似巨多人爭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n城大下學年開辦全港首個自資獸醫學學士課程，現已收到600人申請，中學生與已持有大學學位的申請者各佔一半，其中更有4名申請者持博士學位。校方將根據申請者的成績挑選約60人進行面試，最快於下月（3月）中旬得知是否獲錄取。由於校方首年只開10個學位，故意味平均60人爭一個學位。<br />\n<br />\n有博士學位都讀獸醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有一年學費要12萬，課程唔係UGC資助，grant上限差唔多8萬。<br />\n睇下課程下場會唔會好似理大動物護理學。"},{"pid":"9f172fb353980b89a757b707831e9d94203a4607","tid":183414,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:48:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好揾錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你學識科學方法<br />\n<br />\n較好D養殖參數, 生長周期短左, 肉質好左, 龍蝦健康左, <br />\n<br />\n真係發達野黎<br />\n<br />\n香港都出過嘉美雞, 有乜唔可能"},{"pid":"97a0b3168eae852181da8a863c73c4fd949c11bd","tid":183414,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:50:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"404c956b87ed5fce4a9ea656dba5307dcdf73ea6","tid":183414,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:51:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>獸醫? 有冇牌?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n由城大和美國康奈爾大學合作開辦的全港首個自資獸醫學學士課程，城大昨透露，近日獲澳洲的澳新獸醫管理局理事會(AVBC)發出合理保證書，意味校方能以臨時認證資格，在今年內招收第一屆學生，預計首批畢業生在6年課程畢業後，可以直接取得由澳洲當局認證的獸醫資格，能夠在本地以及英聯邦國家執業。"},{"pid":"ec5b874153f4491e54d9db084c535e552af3c55c","tid":183414,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:53:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好揾錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你學識科學方法<br />\n<br />\n較好D養殖參數, 生長周期短左, 肉質好左, 龍蝦健康左, <br />\n<br />\n真係發達野黎<br />\n<br />\n香港都出過嘉美雞, 有乜唔可能</blockquote><br />\n岩呀 大生意黎 調理農務系 都係 可惜香港農業識微<br />\n外國地大物博 科學化同機械化既農業係一個好大既產業黎<br />\n所以睇財經新聞會成日講非農指數 就係以農民就業同非農民就業黎分 可想而知個產業規模幾咁大"},{"pid":"97f839687917f434f3fbcdc7ab98a9e27e860cad","tid":183414,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:53:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好揾錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你學識科學方法<br />\n<br />\n較好D養殖參數, 生長周期短左, 肉質好左, 龍蝦健康左, <br />\n<br />\n真係發達野黎<br />\n<br />\n香港都出過嘉美雞, 有乜唔可能</blockquote><br />\n嘉美雞個老細好似做左幾十年 TA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d75b51135220fecf85638f8271adcfd77a1cae2","tid":183414,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:55:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好揾錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你學識科學方法<br />\n<br />\n較好D養殖參數, 生長周期短左, 肉質好左, 龍蝦健康左, <br />\n<br />\n真係發達野黎<br />\n<br />\n香港都出過嘉美雞, 有乜唔可能</blockquote><br />\n岩呀 大生意黎 調理農務系 都係 可惜香港農業識微<br />\n外國地大物博 科學化同機械化既農業係一個好大既產業黎<br />\n所以睇財經新聞會成日講非農指數 就係以農民就業同非農民就業黎分 可想而知個產業規模幾咁大</blockquote><br />\n依家講緊vertical farming<br />\n都唔係以前既耕田啦<br />\n<br />\n你搞掂D參數, 科學化去種, 養到自己一半人口<br />\n星加坡就係用vertical farming養到自己一半人口"},{"pid":"9bf87872c81cd247b6c5b4dca01d22cee7af6ffc","tid":183414,"uid":52071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-